	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Gratiam et pacem etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">De substituendo alio in locum <persName ref="p8401">Contzeni</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Zur Debatte um die Nachfolge des verstorbenen <persName ref="p8401">Peter Kunz</persName> s. zuletzt oben <ref target="file11900">Nr. 1854</ref>.</note> nichil dum actum est, siquidem data opera ego negotium distuli usque ad adventum consulis <persName ref="p2305">Negelini</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p2305">Hans Franz Nägeli</persName>.</note> et<pb type="edition" next="124"/> <persName ref="p4217">Augspurgeri</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Welsch-Seckelmeister <persName ref="p4217">Michael Ougspurger</persName>.</note>, qui nunc in provintia sunt <placeName ref="l2478">Sabaudie</placeName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist das 1536 von <placeName ref="l41">Bern</placeName> eroberte savoyische Gebiet.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Sed diutius differre non possum, quoniam <persName ref="p3099">Sultzerus</persName> causam maxime urget.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Proinde ne detrectes, si quem habes, cum quo ecclesie nostre consultum iudicares.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">De <persName ref="p8412">Megandro</persName> nostro multi male sperant ob veterem inimicitiam quorundam;<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p8412">Megander</persName> hatte <placeName ref="l41">Bern</placeName> Anfang 1538 im Streit verlassen, nachdem er schon vorher verschiedentlich angefeindet worden war; s. <bibl source="b1">HBBW I</bibl> <ref target="file10067">[Nr. 39]</ref> 214f, Anm. 53; Matthias <hi>Freudenberg,</hi> Art. <persName ref="p8412">Megander, Kaspar</persName>, in: <bibl source="b93">BBKL</bibl> XIV 1245-1249.</note> tamen<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">tamen <hi>korrigiert aus</hi> tametsi.</note>, si fieri potest, ego non cedam mea diligentia.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Deinde sunt, qui de <persName ref="p1804">Iodoco Kilchmeyr</persName> mentionem fecerunt, quem ego non novi; sed quia <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinus</placeName> est,<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" ana="bio" n="6"><persName ref="p1804">Jodocus Kilchmeyer</persName> stammte zwar aus <placeName ref="l300">Luzern</placeName>, war aber schon seit 1531 Pfarrer im <placeName ref="l803">zürcherischen</placeName> <placeName ref="l270">Küsnacht</placeName>. Er sollte erst nach <persName ref="p2810">Ritters</persName> Tod (1546) nach <placeName ref="l41">Bern</placeName> berufen werden; s. <bibl source="b5">HBBW III</bibl> <ref target="file10262">[Nr. 231]</ref> 137, Anm. 1.</note> multis spem facit egregiam.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Ego, mi <persName ref="p495">Bullingere</persName>, te rogo, ut unum et alterum nomines, quos pro ecclesia nostra esse iudicabis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Deinde, quod putas, te scripturum ad <persName ref="p3099">Sultzerum</persName>, non possum dissuadere; sed caute scribas<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">scribas <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note>, quoniam non dubito vel literas vel descriptum brevi fore <placeName ref="l491">Argentorati</placeName>; ita addictus est <persName ref="p1974">Luthero</persName><note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Vgl. oben <ref target="file11901">Nr. 1855</ref>, Anm. 3.</note> et <persName ref="p467">Buccero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Salutant te et <persName ref="p8412">Megandrum</persName> omnes boni et pii viri.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l41">Berna</placeName>, 11. martii 1544.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p2810">Erasmus Ritter</persName>, ex animo tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Doctissimo simul et pientissimo viro Magistro <persName ref="p495">Henrichio Bullingero</persName>, ecclesie <placeName ref="l587">Tigurine</placeName> antistiti clarissimo etc.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
